videos.headline: Ehlinger finds Duvernay to put Texas on the board
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger puts the ball in the corner of the end zone and finds Devin Duvernay to put Texas on the board in the second.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger finds Duvernay to put Texas on the board) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger's 2nd TD pass extends Texas' lead
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger completes a 17-yard pass to Jake Smith for a touchdown to put Texas up 14-3.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger’s 2nd TD pass extends Texas’ lead) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sanders' TD puts OSU within 1
videos.description: Spencer Sanders 7-yard rushing TD cuts Texas' lead to 14-13.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sanders’ TD puts OSU within 1) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas answers back with 73-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger launches a long pass to Brennan Eagles who takes it all the way for a touchdown, putting Texas up 21-13.

videos.headline: Chuba Hubbard run for 1 yd for a TD (Matt Ammendola KICK)
videos.description: C. Hubbard run for 1 yd for a TD, (M. Ammendola KICK)

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (OC fired up after OSU converts muffed punt ) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas regains lead on trick play
videos.description: Texas runs a reverse flea flicker that ends in Sam Ehlinger's 25-yard touchdown pass to Cade Brewer to go up 28-23.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas regains lead on trick play) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger: 'We knew this team was different'
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger says this year's Texas team knows they are better than previous years' and that belief fueled them to snap the Longhorns' five-game home losing streak against Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Ehlinger: ‘We knew this team was different’) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger dominates OSU with another Heisman worthy performance
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger records his third four-touchdown game of the season, leading Texas to a 36-30 win over Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Enhanced (Ehlinger dominates OSU with another Heisman worthy performance ) 2019/09/22 ESHEET
